==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Zemni
<hw>Zem"ni</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>The
blind mole rat (<spn>Spalax typhlus</spn>), native of Eastern Europe and
Asia. Its eyes and ears are rudimentary, and its fur is soft and
brownish, more or less tinged with gray. It constructs extensive
burrows.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Zemstvo</ent>⟦br⟧
